metadata.name: Julia
metadata.description: Roses were suppose to be works of art. The beautiful point where art met human connection, the place in history when humankind and machines can live as one. Unfortunately, some were not so open to these Ai androids joining our society, so they were chased down and beaten, destroyed and extinguished for a crime they did not commit.. a simple crime of existing. The Ai androids were given a new name ... The Red Roses..
